<body>
    <h1>Get Products For Reservations</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"cf1bf6d881d3"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"7ab9f2bf1469"><strong>Category:</strong> Reservations</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"243e7492f8ad" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-Overview">Ov=
erview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b384408da569">The <strong>Get Products for Reservations</str=
ong> action retrieves the list of products that can be ordered for a specif=
ic reservation. Given a reservation, the component looks up the service (e.=
g., accommodation) that the reservation belongs to and returns all availabl=
e products configured for that service.</p>
<p local-id=3D"136b6fc184a8">Only products that are marked as <strong>order=
able by employees</strong> are returned. Default (automatically posted) pro=
ducts are excluded, since they are not meant to be manually ordered.</p>
<p local-id=3D"366a4f63e4f7">Each product is returned as a <strong>value/la=
bel</strong> pair, where the value is the product's unique identifier and t=
he label is the product's name displayed in the property's language. This m=
akes the output ideal for use as a dropdown source in subsequent workflow s=
teps =E2=80=94 for example, letting a user select which product to add to a=
 reservation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c1fbc916-237a-4c5d-b8fb-bdf50b5f9056">
<h2 local-id=3D"8c66f6eb7581" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-InputFields"=
>Input Fields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"43e0e484-864e-45ee-9c0b-40f=
a773680b5" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e16fd0c9-219c-400c-aa6b-754302c62f2a">
<th data-local-id=3D"9da8b0c5-f08a-42f0-9687-4d52bb645a04" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"44cac8b5691e">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"53a19f2a-7d97-423e-874d-9443ca1a8a94" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"bb8cd15dd306">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"bff2139e-012d-4a0f-b3bd-1255442f3ae9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"864b25ffbd04">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5c4ca49d-be2f-47a9-89dc-39e828788beb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a4c04e32b7a5">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"acb183b1-1c72-49bd-97bd-4370d711ca95">
<td data-local-id=3D"e7adb6ba-fe16-42e0-909b-7ade6bd01048" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3200c2cdf5e2"><strong>Reservation ID</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"92581b8e-bfd8-4bb5-9a97-20dba7eef946" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"612016cc7223"><strong>Required</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"919186d1-569c-4a4f-9347-e71b22ea8987" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab5cfd7e90ef">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e583ec66-5858-4049-bff5-48214544c8d2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a24e4f248b13">The unique identifier of the reservation for w=
hich to retrieve available products. This is typically populated dynamicall=
y from a previous step in the workflow (e.g., a reservation trigger or a "G=
et Eligible Arrivals" action).</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"920b0782-4d09-4d98-9159-017d3248ee14">
<h2 local-id=3D"47f948361e95" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-OutputFields=
">Output Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"eaf06f53c5c2">When products are successfully retrieved, the =
following values are available on the <strong>out</strong> output port for =
use in subsequent workflow steps:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4856e1ad-6575-415f-b56e-116=
38be6fd05" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a98a1f65-0326-4f3e-9197-cbd35f3a6da2">
<th data-local-id=3D"d145cf3e-f0db-46ad-a1be-4bd74310d65f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c41d9d8cd351">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f56cb9f1-c341-42cd-8a6a-803106358bfd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ed75891f27a0">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"6344dc5b-34eb-4c0c-b227-8566fc58cb4e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"a60c3409e4f9">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b5f8bbee-e736-4583-bb42-3c949c72a9df">
<td data-local-id=3D"f7fea38c-2088-4cde-9937-16ad807c5abd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"183621788637"><strong>Items</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6b11ba54-6634-4a1c-8d0f-3426799ef929" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"83b75dfb1cda">Array of objects</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"db7d21f8-4c90-455c-8118-1cd2d905d13a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"090a7afe3f03">A list of available products for the reservati=
on. Each item in the array contains:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"222561b8-7677-4f63-80f5-e67c6f24dba2">
<li local-id=3D"2cbb1b1a-9652-486c-b0f0-f6a9787c2be1">
<p local-id=3D"88c29c5378e7"><strong>Value</strong> =E2=80=94 The unique id=
entifier (GUID) of the product. Use this value when passing the product to =
other components (e.g., "Add Product to Reservation").</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b681b0a9-ab11-4dfc-85d5-c1899b89f8c0">
<p local-id=3D"ffca91629e38"><strong>Label</strong> =E2=80=94 The localized=
 display name of the product, shown in the language configured for the prop=
erty.</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"1dba5254fe9f"><strong>Note:</strong> If no orderable product=
s are configured for the reservation's service, the <strong>Items</strong> =
array will be empty.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a39c2ce1-d071-4ee7-9819-b1f7e9d00f42">
<h2 local-id=3D"7387378d89f3" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-HowItWorks">=
How It Works</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"da54950a-033f-4683-b1a4-aeb0e219ef90">
<li local-id=3D"b09849e5-0bf5-429a-b135-f241bae5bf53">
<p local-id=3D"c879c2556b9e">The component receives the <strong>Reservation=
 ID</strong> from the previous step in the workflow (or from a manually con=
figured value).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2d6ed81-b859-4c9c-8c27-6c5f394d1754">
<p local-id=3D"bf681330ab67">The system looks up the reservation and identi=
fies which <strong>service</strong> (e.g., accommodation) it belongs to. It=
 also verifies that the reservation belongs to the current property.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"2579afe8-707a-418f-b57b-44e90f388089">
<p local-id=3D"41ea262b2b8f">If the reservation is not found or does not be=
long to the property, the component returns an error.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d75db44b-8eb9-442e-abe5-2e4f93c3daad">
<p local-id=3D"d8cae3f8a3e8">The system then queries all <strong>active pro=
ducts</strong> associated with that service, filtering to include only:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"db385f13-eeda-4cf0-bce2-067cd191ca93">
<li local-id=3D"ba54e9a1-c92b-4fac-a282-2de7c35dc122">
<p local-id=3D"959224f18e11">Products that are <strong>orderable by employe=
es</strong> (i.e., products configured to be available for manual ordering =
by staff).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4942c83b-d25d-42a3-9169-1f0c7c765fd0">
<p local-id=3D"e0c7727dd28f">Products that are <strong>not default</strong>=
 (default products are automatically posted and are not intended for manual=
 selection).</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"0493c8a9-3034-401e-9139-c487736e0375">
<p local-id=3D"396bb08f38c2">Each matching product is returned with its uni=
que identifier and its localized name.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4db389e8-ed10-4480-bc2e-62b4122c1a30">
<p local-id=3D"654fe7bba355">The list of products is sent to the <strong>ou=
t</strong> output port.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"9310633a-7d5f-4845-b4be-2ac0ed8a48a5">
<h2 local-id=3D"faec5eb66701" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-ExampleUseCa=
ses">Example Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a4440385-791e-4720-a4ca-8fc5aaa9e43f">
<li local-id=3D"8c15f63c-b0ce-4561-a996-f3645b4d0682">
<p local-id=3D"09af982db26a"><strong>Product selection dropdown</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Use this component to populate a dynamic dropdown in a subsequent=
 step, allowing users to select which product to add to a reservation.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"7f280ce6-5573-4a5a-9ce3-4ba4ed0118ec">
<p local-id=3D"740d6d6dc49d"><strong>Automated product ordering</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Combine with the "Add Product to Reservation" action to automatic=
ally add a specific product to a reservation when certain conditions are me=
t (e.g., a VIP guest arrives).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e2934d0-9917-4427-b9f5-f9692329966e">
<p local-id=3D"0d8f05276085"><strong>Product availability check</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Use the output to verify whether specific products are available =
for a reservation before proceeding with a workflow.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"84f5ce3d-c324-44ca-ba6e-84def2b038a9">
<h2 local-id=3D"7b900a466e17" id=3D"GetProductsForReservations-ErrorHandlin=
g">Error Handling</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7d2ec3b0-c3f7-4f7b-86f2-6f0=
f3d887330" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"77388670-902d-4c94-9e3d-0c4e4993ca89">
<th data-local-id=3D"a8180768-f7c2-4560-aba7-42dac31a7fc3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"8cb58ee574f0">Error</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"9bd21c19-0718-47b1-b491-4cebe1cd33e0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"871ab9f8f623">Cause</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b8fc56ee-6825-4128-a02b-2b77e421e881">
<td data-local-id=3D"36228439-2341-4fa3-8243-f03da1815e60" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3e8f7e20e471"><code>Reservation '{id}' was not found</code><=
/p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d589be52-622c-4ede-8dbf-65341841a6ba" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3d4df3230206">The provided Reservation ID does not match any=
 active reservation in the current property. This can happen if the ID is i=
ncorrect, the reservation has been deleted, or it belongs to a different pr=
operty.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
